## 7️⃣ Custom Hooks + Currying

### ✅ Problem

Reuse hook logic with configuration.

### ✅ Curried Custom Hook

```js
const useFetchWithBaseUrl = baseUrl => endpoint => {
  const [data, setData] = React.useState(null);

  React.useEffect(() => {
    fetch(`${baseUrl}${endpoint}`)
      .then(res => res.json())
      .then(setData);
  }, [endpoint]);

  return data;
};
```

### ✅ Usage

```js
const useApi = useFetchWithBaseUrl("/api");
const users = useApi("/users");
```

✅ Powerful abstraction  
✅ Clean hook API

